OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGenerally dry with some hazy
OL,6,Fsunshine through the morning. Cloud
OL,7,Fincreasing into the afternoon with a
OL,8,Frisk of rain, perhaps turning heavier
OL,9,Fand thundery into the evening. Light
OL,10,For gentle winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain, initially
OL,13,Fpersistent with some heavier bursts,
OL,14,Fwill gradually weaken overnight to
OL,15,Fleave a cloudy, damp start to Tuesday,
OL,16,Fwith hill fog across the Pennines.
OL,17,FWinds remaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
