OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FGradually brightening after a
OL,6,Fcloudy, damp start, and eventually
OL,7,Ffeeling warmer. However, thicker cloud
OL,8,Fand rain returning from the west
OL,9,Fthrough the evening. Turning breezier
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FOften
OL,13,Frather cloudy and breezy during this
OL,14,Fperiod, with outbreaks of rain at
OL,15,Ftimes. The best of any sunshine
OL,16,Fperhaps on Thursday, and east of
OL,17,Fhills. Gradually turning warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
